            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>4</column>
                <head>Free Negroes</head>
                <origin>Richmond Whig</origin>
                <commentary>We are glad to see the Richmond Whig defending the most defenseless
                    class of our population.</commentary>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Whig says Free Negroes are the least likely class to undertake an
                    insurrection; they should not be targetted. Economically useful, if not a
                    profitable class.</summary>
            </div>
